lead_paragraph: Kenenisa Bekele took a swipe at the Ethiopian Athletics Federation on Wednesday after he was left off the marathon team for the Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, calling his exclusion "unjust" and claiming the selection criteria is "biased."

headline.print_headline: Bekele Says 'Unjust' That He Was Left Off Olympic Team
